data.description: DON'T WAIT! This beautiful ranch-style home, nestled in the growing southeast side of Grand Rapids, is looking for its next owner! The main floor has been tastefully refreshed with new paint, lighting, and reclaimed hardwood floors. You'll fall in love with the kitchen complete with new appliances, cabinets, countertops, and backsplash.  This home offers three bedrooms, 2 full baths. There is also a convenient mudroom for hanging coats and removing shoes. The finished basement has a large family room/ rec room, craft room or office area, bath and plenty of storage space.   Newer roof and siding in 2021, bathroom was remodeled in 2023, kitchen in 2018. This one won't last long! Call today for your personal showing! Buyer/Buyer's agent to verify all information.
